snippet.title: Command & Conquer™ Beyond the Battle: Part 2
snippet.description:
Sign up for the beta at http://www.CommandAndConquer.com 

In Part 2 of Beyond the Battle, we take a look at the development of an iconic GLA unit for the new Command & Conquer -- from concept to art production to implementation. Join us behind the scenes for new reveals, never before seen footage, and exclusive interviews from the lead developers of Victory Games.
